---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="安裝 OpenClaw" lang="zh" currentPath="/zh/guide/install" description="選擇你的作業系統安裝 OpenClaw：macOS、Windows 或 VPS/Linux。">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge badge-orange">安裝指南</span>
      <h1>安裝 OpenClaw</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">選擇你的平台開始安裝。每份指南都針對你的環境量身定制，提供逐步操作說明。</p>
      <div class="lang-notice">
        <a href="/guide/install">🇺🇸 Read in English</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="platform-chooser">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="chooser-grid">

        <a href="/zh/guide/install-mac" class="platform-card">
          <div class="platform-icon">🍎</div>
          <h2>macOS</h2>
          <div class="platform-version">適合用 MacBook 或 iMac 的人，安裝最簡單</div>
          <p>Mac 用戶最佳選擇 — 從開始到 AI 上線不到 10 分鐘，步驟最少。像裝 LINE 一樣簡單，不需要寫程式。</p>
          <ul>
            <li>所有選項中最簡單的安裝</li>
            <li>自動在背景運行，不用一直開著終端機</li>
            <li>含完整步驟說明</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="platform-cta">
            macOS 安裝指南 <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/guide/install-windows" class="platform-card">
          <div class="platform-icon">🪟</div>
          <h2>Windows</h2>
          <div class="platform-version">適合用 Windows 電腦的人，需要多一個小步驟（約 10 分鐘）</div>
          <p>Windows 用戶的安裝方式。需要多一個小步驟建立 Linux 環境，全程自動化，不複雜。</p>
          <ul>
            <li>支援 Windows 10 和 11</li>
            <li>設定全自動，照著做就好</li>
            <li>不會影響你現有的檔案或程式</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="platform-cta">
            Windows 安裝指南 <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/guide/install-vps" class="platform-card recommended">
          <div class="platform-badge">⭐ 24/7 運行推薦</div>
          <div class="platform-icon">🖥️</div>
          <h2>VPS / 雲端伺服器</h2>
          <div class="platform-version">適合想讓 AI 24 小時不休息的人，每月費用約 150-250 台幣</div>
          <p>最適合想讓 AI 全天候運行的人。AI 住在雲端，你的電腦關掉它還是在線。</p>
          <ul>
            <li>AI 永遠在線，即使你的電腦關掉也沒問題</li>
            <li>安裝後全程雲端運行，不佔你電腦效能</li>
            <li>不耗你的手機或電腦電池</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="platform-cta">
            VPS 安裝指南 <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="comparison-table">
        <h3>不確定選哪個？</h3>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>比較項目</th>
              <th>macOS</th>
              <th>Windows (WSL2)</th>
              <th>VPS</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>設定難度</td>
              <td>⭐ 簡單</td>
              <td>⭐⭐ 中等</td>
              <td>⭐⭐ 中等</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>24/7 運行</td>
              <td>Mac 開著才能用</td>
              <td>WSL 開著才能用</td>
              <td class="highlight">✅ 永遠在線</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>每月費用</td>
              <td>$0（用你的 Mac）</td>
              <td>$0（用你的 PC）</td>
              <td>每月 $4–8</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>電池影響</td>
              <td>有（背景程序）</td>
              <td>有（背景程序）</td>
              <td class="highlight">✅ 無</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>最適合</td>
              <td>試用體驗</td>
              <td>Windows 用戶</td>
              <td class="highlight">正式生產使用</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero { background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,107,53,0.08) 0%, transparent 100%); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }
  .page-hero .badge { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lang-notice { margin-top: 1rem; }
  .lang-notice a { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .platform-chooser { padding: 4rem 0 5rem; }
  .chooser-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .platform-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2.5rem 2rem; text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); position: relative; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .platform-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255,107,53,0.15); opacity: 1; }
  .platform-card.recommended { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .platform-badge { position: absolute; top: -0.75rem; left: 1.5rem; background: var(--accent); color: white; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 999px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .platform-icon { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .platform-card h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .platform-version { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--accent2); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: var(--mono); }
  .platform-card p { font-size: 0.93rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .platform-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; flex: 1; }
  .platform-card ul li { padding: 0.3rem 0 0.3rem 1.5rem; position: relative; color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.88rem; }
  .platform-card ul li::before { content: "✓"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #4ade80; font-weight: 700; }
  .platform-cta { font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); font-size: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: auto; }
  .arrow { transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .platform-card:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }
  .comparison-table { margin-top: 1rem; overflow-x: auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; }
  .comparison-table h3 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  th, td { padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  th { background: var(--bg2); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--text2); }
  td { color: var(--text2); }
  td:first-child { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
  td.highlight { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .chooser-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } table { font-size: 0.8rem; } th, td { padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem; } }


  /* Mobile layout hardening for install pages */
  .page-hero .container,
  .page-content .container { padding-left: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; }
  .article,
  .article-section,
  .terminal-preview,
  .tip-box,
  .info-box,
  .success-box,
  .warning-box,
  .error-box,
  .support-note,
  .advanced-details,
  .tailscale-box { max-width: 100%; }
  .article pre,
  .article code,
  .terminal-body,
  pre code { overflow-x: auto; max-width: 100%; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-content .container { max-width: 48rem; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; padding-left: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; }
    .article-section { margin-bottom: 2.4rem; }
  }
</style>
